{"tid":1135192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恐怖滑梯奪命！親子14人飛出 釀2死12傷","createTime":"2019-05-02T07:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T06:11:54.000Z","uid":184449,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a1e64cb7c980a41485bbcc77ec946aa1b2729d8b","tid":1135192,"uid":184449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:08:45.000Z","msg":"四川天府新區太平鎮親子樂園「孩子的院子」，昨日下午5時許發生奪命事故。14名成人及兒童在玩「超級滑梯」時，衝出防護設施，其中2名成人送院搶救後不治，餘下12人則仍在醫院接受治療。當地電視台隨後踢爆，事發時，樂園為違規營業。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190502&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59553404\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190502%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59553404&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJuyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=1dbc154a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190502%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59553404&h=b091a708\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190502&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59553404</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WLvY8cp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWLvY8cp.gif&h=23835515&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07b7735700213c4f01e9263c4e29ca7dce4c0a48","tid":1135192,"uid":7043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:11:02.000Z","msg":"絕頂升天<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4dfc2e744beeebf6a1ac1235e675292b44a200d","tid":1135192,"uid":199162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:18:29.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2453e0bd508cfc803839fd05e1b985e018c6d80","tid":1135192,"uid":2772,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201